      "value": "<p>You may spend a spell point to gain a sense that warns you of impending danger. You are not flat-footed during the surprise round or the first round of combat before you act, and gain a +1 dodge bonus to AC, and a +2 bonus to Reflex saves and initiative checks. These bonuses increase by 1 for every 10 caster levels possessed.</p>\n<p><strong>Normal:</strong> You are flat-footed until you have acted once in the initiative order.</p>\n",
